Text: I am looking for someone to seed this torrent permanently instead of me. If you're up to that - post a comment here. I am planning to stop seeding in a week or two.

If you can leave it seeding long enough for me to get both season 3 and 4 then I will be able to seed them both for a long time. I normally don't take things off of my seeding list for a month or two.
While "month or two" is not very long from my point of view, it's still better than nothing, so - thank you. Post here after you complete both seasons.
Hej hej! Snälla seeda alla seasongerna av turtles vore jätte snällt! Är dom på engelska eller ryska? :S
